                },
                {
                    "type": "CallExpression",
                    "name": "setDesc",
                    "source": "Requires restart of Obsidian. If enabled, when the cursor is in a table, enter advances to the next row. Disabling this can help avoid conflicting with tag or CJK autocompletion. If disabling, bind \"Go to ...\" in the Obsidian Hotkeys settings.",
                    "target": "需要重新啟動 Obsidian。啟用後，當游標位於表格中時，按下 Enter 鍵將跳至下一列。停用此功能可避免與標籤或中日韓（CJK）自動完成功能產生衝突。若選擇停用，請在 Obsidian「快速鍵」設定中綁定「移至...」功能。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "CallExpression",
                    "name": "setDesc",
                    "source": "Requires restart of Obsidian. If enabled, when the cursor is in a table, tab/shift+tab navigate between cells. Disabling this can help avoid conflicting with tag or CJK autocompletion. If disabling, bind \"Go to ...\" in the Obsidian Hotkeys settings.",
                    "target": "需要重新啟動 Obsidian。啟用後，當游標位於表格中時，按下 Tab 或 Shift+Tab 鍵可在儲存格之間進行導覽。停用此功能可避免與標籤或中日韓（CJK）自動完成功能產生衝突。若選擇停用，請在 Obsidian「快速鍵」設定中綁定「移至...」功能。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "CallExpression",
